<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ابْتِغَاءَ}</span> ... طَلَبَ تَفْسِيرِه عَلَى مَذَاهِبِهِمِ المُنْحَرِفَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
